{{Top|rwm|title=''Star Wars'' Halloween Audiocast}}
The '''''Star Wars'' Halloween Audiocast''' was an audiocast recorded by [[Matthew Wood]] as [[Grievous/Legends|General Grievous]] and released on [[StarWars.com]] for Halloween of [[2005]]. Initially, it was available only to [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]] members, but beginning [[October 26]], [[2006]], it was made available for download to all readers of the site. It was re-released on the site on [[October 31]], [[2014]].

